snippet.title: HYPERCHARGE: Unboxed - Update Trailer - Future Games Show Gamescom 2022
snippet.description:
Hypercharge: Unboxed is a solo and co-op wave-based first/third-person shooter with a small twist: you're an action figure! Explore. Defend. Survive.

Hypercharge Unboxed is out now on PC and Nintendo Switch, with an Xbox and PlayStation release coming soon.
